# BuildNow GG â€“ Violentmonkey Tweaks

A fullscreen-safe userscript for BuildNow GG that adds:

- FPS counter (works in fullscreen & pointer lock)
- Fully customizable crosshair
- Keyboard shortcuts
- Performance optimizations
- Lightweight & safe

## Features

| Feature | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| FPS Counter | Shows FPS in a fixed overlay, works in fullscreen |
| Crosshair | Fully customizable size, thickness, and color |
| Keybinds | Toggle FPS, toggle crosshair, adjust size/color, reset |
| Performance | Reduces animations and transitions for smoother gameplay |
| UI Cleanup | Removes ads, popups, and clutter |

## Default Keybinds

| Key | Action |
|-----|--------|
| C | Toggle crosshair |
| F | Toggle FPS counter |
| + / - | Increase / decrease crosshair size |
| [ / ] | Decrease / increase thickness |
| H | Cycle crosshair color |
| R | Reset crosshair and FPS |

## Installation

1. Install **Violentmonkey** in your browser  
2. Go to the **Raw URL** of the `buildnow-gg.user.js` file in this repo  
3. Click **Install** in Violentmonkey  
4. Go to https://buildnow.gg and enjoy fullscreen-safe tweaks

## Notes

- Works in fullscreen and pointer lock  
- Client-side visuals only, no cheats or gameplay modification  

